{
  "stem": "3721.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The Hungarians marched in with some Germans, and they dismembered Czechoslovakia as we knew it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At that time, not too much, really.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because my father was an officer in the Austro-Hungarian army.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was quite a decorated one.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the ethnic Hungarians came to him and talked to him, you know, sort of, oh-- don't forget, the Hungarian troops marched in.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the Hungarians looked at them as liberators.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I looked at them as occupiers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the Czech army was a very modern, updated version at that time-- probably the most modern army in Europe.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the Hungarians brought in a rag-tag army that looked something like from a relic of World War I.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I remember quite a few Hungarian and German people of the community, who were very antisemitic, greeted them and, and sort of encouraging them.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We have many Jews that you have to take care of.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "About 15 years old.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not very good.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It felt very uncomfortable.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I sort of was born in Czechoslovakia of Jewish faith, but I-- my loyalty was to the state.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No matter what the state would have been.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But so happened that I was a Czechoslovakian.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My loyalty was to them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- Although, my father didn't feel the same way, because he was born in the Austro-Hungarian monarchy, in the same city.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But there was a-- so he had memories, and especially that he was an officer in the Austro-Hungarian army.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It meant something to him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "To me, it didn't mean anything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, yes, I felt that I lost something right then and there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not only security, but also something that I was-- I grew up with and something that I had loyalty to.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Especially felt uneasy about the threats that these classmates of mine made against another classmate.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
